OL,3,CRefuse workers among council staff to
OL,4,Cstrike over Christmas period
OL,6,FCouncil workers including refuse and
OL,7,Fgrounds maintenance staff are to stage
OL,8,Fa series of strikes over the festive
OL,9,Fperiod in a dispute over pay.
OL,11,FMembers of the GMB union in Waltham
OL,12,FForest, London, will walk out between
OL,13,FDecember 10-12, 17-19, 22-23 and
OL,14,FJanuary 2 and January 5-9.
OL,16,FThe outsourced workers are employed by
OL,17,FFCC Environment, on behalf of Waltham
OL,18,FForest Council.
