OL,3,CRefuse workers among council staff to
OL,4,Cstrike over Christmas period
OL,6,FA recent ballot saw 97% of
OL,7,Fparticipating GMB members vote for
OL,8,Fstrike action, which the union said
OL,9,Fwill affect refuse collection and
OL,10,Fstreet cleaning in the borough.
OL,12,FMary Goodson, GMB regional organiser,
OL,13,Fsaid: "Our members still have not been
OL,14,Foffered a decent pay uplift, leaving
OL,15,Fthem no choice but to take strike
OL,16,Faction."
