OL,3,CRefuse workers among council staff to
OL,4,Cstrike over Christmas period
OL,6,FCouncillor Clyde Loakes, the council's
OL,7,Fdeputy leader and cabinet member for
OL,8,Fclimate and air quality, said: "We are
OL,9,Fdisappointed by the lack of a
OL,10,Fresolution to this long-running pay
OL,11,Fnegotiation.
OL,13,F"We urge both parties to continue with
OL,14,Fthe dialogue that has seen
OL,15,Fimprovements made to the offer so far.
OL,17,F"The discussions remain between FCC
OL,18,FEnvironment and its staff and are not
OL,19,Fwithin the council's jurisdiction.
